'''Hisashi Igawa''' (井川比佐志 born [[17 November]] [[1936]]) is a Japanese actor who has appeared in such films as [[Akira Kurosawa]]'s ''[[Dodesukaden]]'', ''[[Ran (film)|Ran]]'' and ''[[Madadayo]]''.

